Package: lls
Type: Package
Title: Local Least Squares Estimation for Information Provision Experiments
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Dylan Balla-Elliott <dballaelliott@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Dylan Balla-Elliott <dballaelliott@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dylan", "Balla-Elliott", email = "dballaelliott@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Implements the Local Least Squares (LLS) estimator for identifying 
    causal effects in information provision experiments. The LLS estimator 
    consistently estimates Average Partial Effects (APE) even when there is 
    strong dependence between belief updating and belief effects. Includes 
    plotting functions for visualizing results with binned estimates and 
    confidence intervals.
